Topic: Using book reviews to create a recommendation systems that would look at a user's interest and suggest highly rated books in that genre.

Reason: Netflix, Hulu and many other streaming platforms use a recommendation system to keep users interested. For example each Neftlix users has different recommedations for 
  shows and movies based of their age and demographic. 
  
Datasourse: Kaggle 
  https://www.kaggle.com/arashnic/book-recommendation-dataset
  https://www.kaggle.com/snanilim/book-recommendation-engine/data?select=books.csv
    CSV files that will be joined together to create dataset of book reviews.
    
 Questions we hope to answer: How a user's information like interests be used to customize recommendations.  
